# Help for ~remort~

~remort~ resets your progression into a new path inspired by classic DarkPawns remort gameplay.

## Usage:

  ~remort~  
  ~remort confirm~

Run ~remort~ to view requirements and your current remort path.

Run ~remort confirm~ to complete the ritual.

## Requirements:

- Must be at or above the configured remort level.
- Must have enough gold for the remort cost.
- Must not be wearing equipment.
- May require being in a room tagged for remort rituals.

## Notes:

- Your level, XP, trained skills, active buffs, and cooldowns are reset.
- You receive a remort starter skill package based on your strongest profession.
